ʻAʻole hoʻokomo ʻia ʻo Whatsapp. E ʻoluʻolu e hoʻokomo iā Whatsapp e hoʻohana i kēia hiʻohiʻona.
Ua ālai ʻia ka papa keyboard. E kaomi i ka ikona keyboard e wehe ai.

1. E wehe i ka polokalamu Whats Web ma kāu kelepona.

2. E wehe i ka whatsapp ma nā kelepona ʻē aʻe.

* Ma ka Android -> Mai ka pale kamaʻilio, e hele i ka papa kuhikuhi ʻekolu kiko ma ka ʻaoʻao ʻākau o ka pale -> Nā mea pili.

* Ma ke kelepona puka aniani -> E hele i ka papa kuhikuhi kiko ʻekolu -> Nā mea pili.

* Ma iPhone -> E hele i nā ʻōkuhi -> nā mea pili.

3. E kāomi i ka loulou i kahi mea hana a nānā i ka QR Code i hōʻike ʻia ma kāu pale app mai ke kelepona ʻē aʻe.
